author: @sebastianglints
content:
Madonna has 4 daughters. Lourdes was her first one and she is her only biological daughter. Playing the piano is Mercy James, her second daughter, adopted. And then she also has 2 little twins, Estere and Stella, both also adopted.
She also has 2 sons, Rocco (biological) and David (adopted).
